precis:
Amendment (SCHEDULE No. 934) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which sets
Maximum Residue Limits on the amount of "GLYPHOSATE" which can be detected
in the kidneys (2.0 ppm) and the liver (0.2 ppm) of cattle, goats, hogs,
poultry and sheep.
